---
title: Thai-Style Turkey 'Pad Krapow' with Green Beans
description: Pad krapow is a popular dish in the Thai street food scene. In our version, ground turkey is stir-fried with aromatic ingredients such as ginger, garlic, lime and chili pepper and served over fluffy rice.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-style-turkey-pad-krapow-beae1ba8.jpg
